{"id":386107,"date":[{"year":1959,"month":3,"day":9}],"page":"3","source":"“星火”","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"123","ytitle":"","mtitle":"你在干什么?","ftitle":"","authors":["阿鼎"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子从学校回家，母亲发现他的新帽子给弄破了，而且满是污泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“怎么搞的?”母亲惊奇地问。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“都怪大哥哥们不好。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大哥哥们怎么啦?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他们脱下我的帽子当足球踢。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“那么你在干什么呢?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我在守门。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(阿鼎译自“星火”1959年第7期)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1959\\03\\5939031301.JPG\">"}]}